tip.text: Awesome places as it has evolved from the 80s to now. Lots of activities and exhibitions to see, observes and experiences. Good fun for the whole family for at least half a day.

formattedAddress: Singapore Science Centre (15 Science Centre Road)

tip.text: A real fun for the family. The sliding area was so cool and fun. It's a small park and the real attraction will be the sliding area.  The rest of the park ain't anything worth to see.
Good place for kids to have fun, suitable for kids below 6, though elder kids can appreciate the climbing & etc. try the Giant J where you are lifted to max 7 meters prior letting go & slide down.
